    <string name="support_title">Support &amp; safety</string>
    <string name="disclaimer_message">MindEase is a supportive companion to help you reflect and feel heard. It is not a therapist, doctor, or crisis service, and it cannot provide diagnosis or treatment.\n\nIf you are in crisis or may be in danger, please contact a qualified professional or your local emergency services right away.\n\nMindEase is not a substitute for professional help.</string>

    <string name="crisis_resources">If you are in immediate danger, call your local emergency number now.\n• Find a helpline worldwide: https://findahelpline.com\n\nYou are not alone, and reaching out is a sign of strength.</string>
